ess should be observed for bronchospasm and secondary pneumonia.<br />\nIn patients with pre-existing respiratory disease, suffering from acute bronchospasm: humidified oxygen, aminophylline, and inhaled sympathomimetics may be necessary.<br />\nSymptoms should subside within 60 minutes of exposure."},{"pid":"609c39a7b797fd036bf89a45d9a6559e2d7c59c5","tid":1417681,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:12:03.000Z","msg":"沖完涼換過晒所有衣物"},{"pid":"3db0cb7ebfcbc3ae0fb7f23da5f872ab13913aea","tid":1417681,"uid":49756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4bd37dfa3c5711fed1c77133044294f7bab05890","tid":1417681,"uid":220351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:10:56.000Z","msg":"烏龍茶"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:12:31.000Z","msg":"用佢沖？"},{"pid":"63e4abadfbf44e2e60f690639d2db808e7264d28","tid":1417681,"uid":14087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"727bf27e1f2c5b1273a30170f2ef2bf97232c9ea","tid":1417681,"uid":49756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6deb202c99e8a6253612af7bed756bab6855f2fe","tid":1417681,"uid":14087,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"6c1ed0003754c3e466784b030040080f90ca5822","tid":1417681,"uid":49756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:58:28.000Z","msg":"手同頸紅撚哂 有小小痛 係咪等佢自然好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:08:00.000Z","msg":"有冇沖涼 <br />\n沖二次沖涼液<br />\n一定要沖耐d 沖乾淨<br />\n洗走哂化學野 再開冷氣攤屍<br />\n有維他命B同c 就照啪 <br />\n飲多杯水 聽日就無咩事 <br />\n我發夢都係咁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:11:27.000Z","msg":"ok 啪返杯唯多C 先"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:13:26.000Z","msg":"最重要係洗乾淨 開冷氣攤c <br />\n唔好有汗up住"},{"pid":"a39b4b7d038e751aaf703f9c2dd1fab6095329d2","tid":1417681,"uid":49756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:13:32.000Z","msg":"我有沖好哂涼啊 thankss咁多位手足 係怕佢會有泡泡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d59d6867629ee4acf182ab1529c811aa0